Full SQL Server compatibility
Supports ETL + analytics workloads

2. Data Integration ($500)

Use: Azure Data Factory
Pipeline Flow: Salesforce → Staging → SQL MI
Cost Control: Use trigger-based pipelines (not continuous)
Optimize activity runs

Salesforce Integration
Use ADF connectors
Incremental loads (very important)
Avoid full loads → saves cost + time

3. Analytics ($800)

Use: Azure Databricks
Strategy: Use job clusters (not always-on clusters)
Start → process → terminate
Pay only for usage

