Cost Optimization Strategy

1. Databricks: Use job clusters only. Avoid idle clusters
2. Data Factory: Schedule pipelines (batch).Use incremental loads
3. SQL Managed Instance: Choose General Purpose tier. Avoid overprovisioning vCores
4. Storage Tiering: Move old data → Cool/Archive
5. Dev/Test Optimization: Stop VMs after hour. Use lower tiers for staging

